Event

   Pyb / Wikimédia commons
   COUR DES COMPTES 24.04.19

The Cour des comptes will control the funds raised for the rebuilding of
Notre-Dame cathedral in Paris

   The Cour des comptes, France’s supreme audit institution, will start to
   control the fundraising, the management of the raised funds and their
   use in the rebuilding of Notre-Dame cathedral in Paris. This control
   will last until the end of the reconstruction and lead to a yearly
   report.
   En savoir plus

